<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3152896" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:ShadowCursor">Activates or deactivates the direct cursor.</ahelp> You can specify the behavior of the direct cursor by choosing <link href="text/shared/optionen/01040600.xhp" name="Tools - Options - Text Document - Formatting Aids"><emph>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Writer - Formatting Aids</emph></link>.</paragraph>
